==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Overload
<hw>O"ver*load`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An excessive load;
the excess beyond a proper load.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overlogical</ent>⟦br⟧
